le":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1322810948,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":-5501,"width":212.41787719726562},{"seed":621628484,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"92exGfa0NIy_2dd-Zttkt","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"startBinding":null,"endArrowhead":null,"opacity":100,"updated":1772873306457,"locked":false,"points":[[0,0],[522,0]],"polygon":false,"version":5,"type":"line","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"aU","roundness":null,"lastCommittedPoint":null,"height":0,"link":null,"startArrowhead":null,"strokeColor":"#e5e7eb","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"endBinding":null,"versionNonce":128481276,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":-5477,"width":522},{"seed":295904196,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"9TT_YBFQGrgg3IGByklej","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306457,"locked":false,"text":"A search autocomplete system returns ranked query\ncompletions as the user types — within 100ms per\nkeystroke. Every major search surface (Google, Amazon,\nYouTube, Maps) runs one. The system predicts user intent\nfrom incomplete prefixes using global query frequency,\nrecency trends, and per-user personalization signals.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"aV","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"A search autocomplete system returns ranked query\ncompletions as the user types — within 100ms per\nkeystroke. Every major search surface (Google, Amazon,\nYouTube, Maps) runs one. The system predicts user intent\nfrom incomplete prefixes using global query frequency,\nrecency trends, and per-user personalization signals.","height":105,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#374151","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2134382020,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":-5469,"width":399.69952392578125},{"seed":747768644,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"LFU75Lma5nuLP92c3vI5F","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306457,"locked":false,"text":"The core tension: billions of new query logs arrive daily\nand must update suggestion rankings without blocking the\n200K+ reads per second happening concurrently at peak.\nThe trie data structure must live almost entirely in memory\n— disk is orders of magnitude too slow for the latency SLA.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"aW","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"The core tension: billions of new query logs arrive daily\nand must update suggestion rankings without blocking the\n200K+ reads per second happening concurrently at peak.\nThe trie data structure must live almost entirely in memory\n— disk is orders of magnitude too slow for the latency SLA.","height":87.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#374151","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1078990972,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":-5331,"width":414.4835205078125},{"seed":1748501188,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"1y84j0VEI8JGJPV1fAVzP","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"startBinding":null,"endArrowhead":null,"opacity":100,"updated":1772873306457,"locked":false,"points":[[0,0],[522,0]],"polygon":false,"version":5,"type":"line","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"aX","roundness":null,"lastCommittedPoint":null,"height":0,"link":null,"startArrowhead":null,"strokeColor":"#e5e7eb","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"endBinding":null,"versionNonce":1052294468,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":-5203,"width":522},{"seed":993200708,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"C-z5GGV8MBPCCyRVgatvY","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306457,"locked":false,"text":"Key Challenges","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"aY","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Key Challenges","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":875538684,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":-5191,"width":125.2799072265625},{"seed":409018820,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"JLqgu23FpBoIQq8HpvxgD","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"startBinding":null,"endArrowhead":null,"opacity":100,"updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"points":[[0,0],[522,0]],"polygon":false,"version":5,"type":"line","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"aZ","roundness":null,"lastCommittedPoint":null,"height":0,"link":null,"startArrowhead":null,"strokeColor":"#e5e7eb","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"endBinding":null,"versionNonce":649622724,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":-5167,"width":522},{"seed":1725974852,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"YDewDLd4uEFRMPck9BVxd","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"text":"Latency: the trie must be entirely in-memory — disk is\n1000x too slow for sub-100ms targets at 200K req\/s.\n\nFreshness: billions of daily logs must update rankings\nwithout blocking concurrent reads — async pipeline required.\n\nHot Prefixes: single trie nodes for \"a\" or \"how to\"\nreceive extreme concentrated load and become bottlenecks.\n\nPersonalization: blending global + per-user signals adds\na state lookup on the sub-100ms critical path.\n\nTrending Queries: breaking news must surface in minutes,\nrequiring near-real-time log ingestion and trie updates.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"aa","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Latency: the trie must be entirely in-memory — disk is\n1000x too slow for sub-100ms targets at 200K req\/s.\n\nFreshness: billions of daily logs must update rankings\nwithout blocking concurrent reads — async pipeline required.\n\nHot Prefixes: single trie nodes for \"a\" or \"how to\"\nreceive extreme concentrated load and become bottlenecks.\n\nPersonalization: blending global + per-user signals adds\na state lookup on the sub-100ms critical path.\n\nTrending Queries: breaking news must surface in minutes,\nrequiring near-real-time log ingestion and trie updates.","height":245,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#374151","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":382282108,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":-5155,"width":407.7354736328125},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"ab","backgroundColor":"#fffbeb","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772873306458,"id":"JJJyZmK3NYCbVaVSKGesd","x":727,"seed":2047770820,"boundElements":[],"y":-4821,"opacity":100,"height":100,"width":526,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1960131652},{"seed":160024644,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"Asa6-OaWvuh_7D1sHVv9g","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"text":"Key insight: Every architectural decision in this system\nis downstream of one constraint — sub-100ms latency.\nDisk is ruled out. The trie lives in distributed memory.\nThis single rule shapes storage, updates, and topology.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"ac","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Key insight: Every architectural decision in this system\nis downstream of one constraint — sub-100ms latency.\nDisk is ruled out. The trie lives in distributed memory.\n