"version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bCn","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Hash: SHA256(part+offset+query)\nStore: trie_updates MySQL 24h TTL\nINSERT IGNORE:\n  1 row = new, apply update\n  0 rows = duplicate, skip","height":75,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#374151","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":819939268,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":415,"angle":0,"y":4043,"width":218.89164733886719},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bCo","backgroundColor":"#fff1f2","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772873306458,"id":"miCD6XVKeykjZSSPhaBLF","x":-109,"seed":206761796,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"NHEdwv6ktluxLyOVTdSAP"}],"y":4129,"opacity":100,"height":44,"width":760,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1164772988},{"seed":1715234500,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"NHEdwv6ktluxLyOVTdSAP","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1772873306471,"locked":false,"text":"DLQ Policy: fires after 5 failed attempts. PagerDuty on first message. Ops review within 4h SLA. Replay or discard\nafter root cause analysis.","version":7,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bCp","roundness":null,"containerId":"miCD6XVKeykjZSSPhaBLF","originalText":"DLQ Policy: fires after 5 failed attempts. PagerDuty on first message. Ops review within 4h SLA. Replay or discard after root cause analysis.","height":32.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":125466308,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-95.912017822265625,"angle":0,"y":4134.75,"width":733.82403564453125},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#c7d2fe","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bCq","backgroundColor":"#f8faff","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1.5,"version":5,"roundness":null,"type":"rectangle","updated":1772873306458,"id":"w5V8CgBcoYZrHpNeD1B_-","x":709,"seed":1124789828,"boundElements":[],"y":3601,"opacity":100,"height":760,"width":562,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":595515132},{"seed":597460420,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"B6r0CBzxg59Z6IAJtU8PU","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"text":"Retry Strategy","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bCr","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Retry Strategy","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2042308292,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":3619,"width":126.92190551757812},{"seed":1024404804,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"FAdG-VJBbnQtjNi3O9EYA","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"startBinding":null,"endArrowhead":null,"opacity":100,"updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"points":[[0,0],[522,0]],"polygon":false,"version":5,"type":"line","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bCs","roundness":null,"lastCommittedPoint":null,"height":0,"link":null,"startArrowhead":null,"strokeColor":"#e5e7eb","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"endBinding":null,"versionNonce":1879218044,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":3643,"width":522},{"seed":1891689668,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"mGG4PGErOFOQEE5gF-iMQ","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"text":"The formula is wait = min(100ms x 2^attempt + jitter,\n30s). Jitter of 0-100ms is critical — without it, all\nclients retry simultaneously after a partial outage\nand create a thundering herd that re-triggers the\nfailure. Five attempts covering ~3.1 seconds is\nchosen because beyond that the user has already\nnavigated away or given up on autocomplete. Retries\napply only to transient errors. Poison messages and\ninfrastructure failures escalate immediately.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bCt","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"The formula is wait = min(100ms x 2^attempt + jitter,\n30s). Jitter of 0-100ms is critical — without it, all\nclients retry simultaneously after a partial outage\nand create a thundering herd that re-triggers the\nfailure. Five attempts covering ~3.1 seconds is\nchosen because beyond that the user has already\nnavigated away or given up on autocomplete. Retries\napply only to transient errors. Poison messages and\ninfrastructure failures escalate immediately.","height":157.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#374151","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2024910404,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":3655,"width":370.1175537109375},{"seed":1146072132,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"0ZYDjaAShBn2M54Pp340_","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"text":"Dead Letter Queue Policy","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bCu","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Dead Letter Queue Policy","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1731872764,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":3815,"width":213.21385192871094},{"seed":1503232964,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"JXkafd1K2q-kG73qeCAtd","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"startBinding":null,"endArrowhead":null,"opacity":100,"updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"points":[[0,0],[522,0]],"polygon":false,"version":5,"type":"line","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bCv","roundness":null,"lastCommittedPoint":null,"height":0,"link":null,"startArrowhead":null,"strokeColor":"#e5e7eb","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"endBinding":null,"versionNonce":1986741700,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":3839,"width":522},{"seed":1723624260,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"jfb11FllasKZ8YEeO2ukv","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"text":"A Kafka message lands in the DLQ after all 5 retry\nattempts fail. PagerDuty fires on the first DLQ\nmessage — even one poisoned message signals a\nschema contract break or unseen edge case. Ops has\na 4-hour SLA to review. The most common cause is\na schema mismatch from a producer deployment before\na consumer deployment. The fix is a consumer hotfix\nor a replay after the schema issue is resolved.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bCw","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"A Kafka message lands in the DLQ after all 5 retry\nattempts fail. PagerDuty fires on the first DLQ\nmessage — even one poisoned message signals a\nschema contract break or unseen edge case. Ops has\na 4-hour SLA to review. The most common cause is\na schema mismatch from a producer deployment before\na consumer deployment. The fix is a consumer hotfix\nor a replay after the schema issue is resolved.","height":140,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#374151","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1831331964,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":3851,"width":369.78158569335938},{"seed":773219012,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"7l_I0ob7O3lrNMQFez-AG","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"text":"Idempotency Implementation","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bCx","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Idempotency Implementation","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1208347972,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":4019,"width":234.97383117675781},{"seed":1984260676,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"owp8t8hH55b5cT9wEYCpl","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"startBinding":null,"endArrowhead":null,"opacity":100,"updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"points":[[0,0],[522,0]],"polygon":false,"version":5,"type":"line","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bCy","roundness":null,"lastCommittedPoint":null,"height":0,"link":null,"startArrowhead":null,"strokeColor":"#e5e7eb","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"endBinding":null,"versionNonce":361593084,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":4043,"width":522},{"seed":36143556,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"vVBO0hiIcnIe7EusaBGMD","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"text":"The key is SHA256(partition_id + offset + normalized\nquery). Partition and offset uniquely identify the\nKafka message. The normalized query is included so\nthat two messages producing identical operations\ncan still be deduplicated. Stored in trie_updates\nMySQL with INSERT IGNORE — zero rows affected means\nduplicate detected, skip the trie update. TTL is 24\nhours, safely covering any Kafka replay window after\na consumer crash and restart.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bCz","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"The key is SHA256(partition_id + offset + normalized\nquery). Partition and offset uniquely identify the\nKafka message. The normalized query is included so\nthat two messages producing identical operations\ncan still be deduplicated. Stored in trie_updates\nMySQL with INSERT IGNORE — zero rows affected means\nduplicate detected, skip the trie update. TTL is 24\nhours, safely covering any Kafka replay window after\na consumer crash and restart.","height":157.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#374151","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1860150468,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":727,"angle":0,"y":4055,"width":407.34356689453125},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bD0","backgroundColor":"#fff1f2","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772873306458,"id":"a731OVPuYLA_z8waHmv4-","x":727,"seed":148547908,"boundElements":[],"y":4219,"opacity":100,"height":110,"width":526,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":736950652},{"seed":767353028,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"bMljjXDSzG8S-t69Xgnq-","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772873306458,"locked":false,"text":"Key insight: Jitter in retry backoff and idempotency\nin Kafka consumers are load-shedding mechanisms,\nnot polish. Without jitter, retries amplify failures.\nWithout idempotency, Kafka replays corrupt the trie\nwith double-counted query frequencies.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bD1","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Key insight: Jitter in retry backoff and idempotency\nin Kafka consumers are load-shedding mechanisms,\nnot polish. Without jitter, retries amplify failures.\nWithout idempotency, Kafka replays corrupt the trie\nwith double-counted query frequencies.","height":87.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#991b1b","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonc